## Specification
Two-file atomic change: create direnv.toml config file and wire it as mkOutOfStoreSymlink in home.nix.

## Files Owned
- CREATE: users/minttea/direnv/direnv.toml
- MODIFY: users/minttea/home.nix (lines 170-183)

## Leaf Tasks
- SLICE-1-L1: Create direnv.toml config file
- SLICE-1-L3: Modify home.nix (remove config block, add xdg.configFile symlink)

## Exact Changes

### CREATE: users/minttea/direnv/direnv.toml
```toml
[global]
hide_env_diff = true

[whitelist]
prefix = [
  "/home/minttea/dev",
  "/home/minttea/codebases/dayvidpham"
]
```

### MODIFY: users/minttea/home.nix

Remove lines 175-182 (the config block). Add xdg.configFile entry after programs.direnv block.

Before (lines 170-183):
```nix
programs.direnv = {
  enable = true;
  enableZshIntegration = true;
  nix-direnv.enable = true;

  config = {
    global = {
      hide_env_diff = true;
    };
    whitelist = {
      prefix = [ "\${home.homeDirectory}/dev/david-agent-data-leverage" ];
    };
  };
};
```

After:
```nix
programs.direnv = {
  enable = true;
  enableZshIntegration = true;
  nix-direnv.enable = true;
};

xdg.configFile."direnv/direnv.toml".source =
  config.lib.file.mkOutOfStoreSymlink
    /home/minttea/dotfiles/users/minttea/direnv/direnv.toml;
```

